    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hi there! \ud83d\udc4b Are you looking for a reliable set of wheels that\u2019s ready for your next adventure? I\u2019m parting with my car, and it has been such a joy to own! It\u2019s in really nice shape, runs like a dream, and has been well-cared for. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a road trip, this beauty is super dependable and ready to go today. Come take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love how it handles! \ud83d\ude97\u2728",
