    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound 2002 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six engine. This unit delivers linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. The high-revving valvetrain remains tight, and the double-VANOS system has been serviced to ensure optimal variable valve timing. The chassis features a factory-limited-slip differential and a subframe that has been inspected for structural integrity. Suspension components maintain their damping characteristics, providing the precise turn-in and lateral stability this platform is known for. Finished in Titanium Silver over Black Nappa leather, it shows honest wear consistent with a well-maintained enthusiast vehicle.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Clean title. Maintenance up to date. Runs well. Inspections welcome.",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
