    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a well-maintained 2017 BMW M3 finished in timeless Alpine White over a striking Sakhir Orange extended leather interior. This vehicle has been my pride and joy, serving as a reliable and exhilarating daily driver. The exterior presents beautifully with a deep gloss, though in the spirit of full transparency, there are a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side wheel\u2014typical for a car that has actually been enjoyed on the road. Inside, the cabin remains a premium environment; the leather is supple and clean, with only slight entry wear on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All electronics, including the Harman Kardon surround sound and navigation system, function perfectly. Mechanically, this M3 is stout. It has been serviced exclusively at certified centers, with a fresh oil change and brake fluid flush completed just last month. The turbocharged inline-six pulls hard and smooth, paired with a crisp DCT transmission. It sits on Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires with plenty of life remaining. This is an honest, solid example of a modern legend, ready for its next enthusiast owner.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive reliability, this vehicle has been meticulously maintained to ensure peak performance and aesthetic integrity. It offers a refined driving experience, characterized by a smooth powertrain and a well-preserved interior. This selection represents a premier opportunity for the discerning buyer seeking a balance of sophistication and enduring value.",
      "price": 34500.0,
