      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my trusty car and it\u2019s been such a fantastic ride. It's in really solid shape and has been super reliable for everything from grocery runs to weekend road trips. It\u2019s been well-loved and looked after, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road with a new owner today. It drives smoothly and looks great\u2014I'm honestly going to miss it! Come take it for a test drive and see for yourself!",
      "price": 31500.0,
